OL,3,CPolice enforce closure of two schools
OL,5,FTwo schools in Cardiff will remain
OL,6,Fclosed on Monday after "a report was
OL,7,Fmade to the police".
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police has implemented the
OL,10,Fmeasures at Llanishen High School and
OL,11,FEastern High School as "a safety
OL,12,Fprecaution."
OL,14,FThe force said it has not taken the
OL,15,Fdecision "lightly" and added that it
OL,16,Fdid so in conjunction with the city's
OL,17,Fcouncil ensure the safety of pupils.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
