OL,3,CPolice enforce closure of two schools
OL,5,FThe nature of the report, which it has
OL,6,Fnot been disclosed, remains under
OL,7,Finvestigation according to police.
OL,8,FNever miss a Cardiff story by signing
OL,9,Fup to our daily newsletter here.
OL,11,FA statement from South Wales Police
OL,12,Fread: "Two Cardiff schools will remain
OL,13,Fclosed on Monday (16 March) following
OL,14,Fa report made to South Wales Police on
OL,15,FSunday evening.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
