OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1773767470
OL,3,CPolice enforce closure of two schools
OL,5,F"Llanishen High School and Eastern
OL,6,FHigh School will close as a safety
OL,7,Fprecaution whilst investigations are
OL,8,Fundertaken, following discussion
OL,9,Fbetween the police and Cardiff
OL,10,FCouncil."
OL,12,FSuperintendent Mark Kavanagh added:
OL,13,F"We have come to the decision, with
OL,14,Fsupport from Cardiff Council, to keep
OL,15,Fthese schools closed on Monday in
OL,16,Forder to avoid risk, following a
OL,17,Freport which was made to police on
OL,18,FSunday evening. This report is
OL,19,Fcurrently under investigation.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
